summary: The document is a historical record pertaining to the JFK assassination system, specifically an identification form for David Reed Fromer, dated December 2, 1966. It details a local agency check conducted in Oakland, California, which found that a David Fromer appeared on two mailing lists of SLATE in November 1966. The document is unclassified but was released with deletions and was last reviewed on March 7, 1995.
